file.name: specWithSchemas.yaml
file.content:
openapi: "3.0.0"
info:
  title: Spec with schemas API
  version: 1
paths:
  /:
    get:
      operationId: listVersionsv2
      responses:
        '200':
          description: returns string
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: string
  /v2:
    get:
      operationId: getVersionDetailsv2
      responses:
        '200':
          description: returns dataset
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/dataSetList'
    post:
      operationId: postVersionDetailsv2
      responses:
        '200':
          description: returns string
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: string
components:
  schemas:
    dataSetList:
      type: object
      properties:
        total:
          type: integer
        apis:
          type: array
          items:
            type: object
            properties:
              apiKey:
                type: string
              apiVersionNumber:
                type: string
              apiUrl:
                type: string
                format: uriref
              apiCount:
                type: integer
                format: int64
              apiAvg:
                type: number
              isInternal:
                type: boolean
              start:
                type: string
                format: date
              apiHash:
                type: string
                format: byte
            required:
              - apiKey
              - apiVersionNumber
              - apiUrl
              - apiCount
              - apiAvg
              - isInternal
              - start
              - apiHash
      required:
        - total
        - apis
